data.title: Traces of Evil: Remaining Nazi Sites in Baden
data.meta_description: The most extensive online site devoted to comparing remaining Nazi sites in Baden-Wrttemberg today, including Friedrichshafen, Mannheim, Ulm and Tbingen, with how they originally appeared before and during the war using unique GIFs, film footage and images
data.text: View from south of Tbingen towards Neckar and Galgenberg
